                        <note rend="inline" type="source">611.6731/106: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Grew</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-05-18T16:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">May 18,
                                        1928—4 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>51. Your 74, May 17, 9 p.m. There is no objection to the modifications
                            proposed by the Minister of Foreign Affairs.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
